{"word":"G1719 - ἔμφοβος - émphobos - em'-fob-os - Affrighted","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔμφοβος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">émphobos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">em'-fob-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Affrighted</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பயப்பட்ட, பயந்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"thrown into fear, terrified, affrighted"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G5401 - φόβος - phóbos - fob'-os/5401\">G5401</a>; <i>in fear</i>, that is, <i>alarmed:</i> - affrighted, afraid, tremble.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}